# Command to easily retrieve and display up to date weather information inside terminal
# Downloads data from the National Weather service weather.noaa.gov in pure text form
# Enter 4-letter ICAO station identifier of station closest to you and replace 'KRIV.TXT' in command with your station id
# Example: curl weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/observations/metar/decoded/your_four_letter_station_id.TXT

# Find 4 letter ICAO station identifier of station nearest you from this list
# http://weather.noaa.gov/data/nsd_cccc.txt


curl weather.noaa.gov.pub/data/observations/metar/decoded/KRIV.TXT
